developments.title: Canadian City
developments.description:
Boasting a prime location and having a category-A NOC from the Gwadar Development Authority (GDA), Canadian City Gwadar offers residential and commercial plots on easy instalments. It has gained immense interest of investors and future home owners alike as it flaunts highly affordable prices coupled with hassle-free purchasing process. Being a part of Gwadar’s revised master plan, Canadian City Gwadar is set to offer remarkable returns on investment. The project is set to deliver an incredible international-standard lifestyle for everyone who envisions a home in Gwadar. Location Highlights:
  • 1.5 km from Makran Coastal Highway
  • 2.5 km from Marine Drive
  • 5 km from Zero Point
  • 15 km from Gwadar International Airport
  • Will be close to top ranking hotels and renowned banks What’s on Offer? A range of property options is up for grabs in Canadian City Gwadar. Currently on offer are the following Residential Plots:
  • 5 Marla
  • 10 Marla
  • 20 Marla
  • 40 Marla Commercial plots of 2-, 4- and 8-marla were also available in the locality, but were sold out within a short period of time. Why invest in Canadian City Gwadar? The following are some reasons why Canadian City Gwadar is a project worthwhile for investment:
  • Category-A NOC
  • Part of Gwadar’s revised Master Plan
  • Property insurance in case of buyer’s accidental death
  • The China-Pakistan Economic Corridor will trigger property prices
  • Zameen. com's search trends show that consumer interest has increased by 235.72% for plots 291.42% for houses and 243.61% for commercial property in Gwadar in the last year
  • Gwadar will be a tax-free zone generating extraordinary revenue from industrial and trade activities
  • Gwadar will be home to around 2.3 million job opportunities in the future, increasing demand for residential and commercial properties
  • Gwadar is positioned along the Gulf and provides direct access to over 70% of the world's sea traffic. China-Pakistan Economic Corridor: Amid other benefits, Gwadar will have the following under the China-Pakistan Economic Corridor project:
  • Diverse investment opportunities
  • Industrial, financial and educational growth
  • Better job opportunities
  • High-quality healthcare facilities
  • Regional connectivity
  • Enhanced security and stability
  • Superior educational institutions
  • Increased volume of trade and investment activities Facilities & Amenities:
  • Efficient and reliable gas, electricity and sewerage system
  • High quality fiber optic cables
  • Sector markets
  • Water treatment plant
  • Top-notch security system
  • Hospital
  • Jamia mosque
  • Swimming pool

developments.title: Hamza Residencia
developments.description:
Hamza Residencia – Experience life at its best! Hamza Residencia is an all-new residential project launched by Hamza Developer in Lahore. Designed as a lavish apartment complex, the structure has been built to provide an elegant and stress-free living experience for its inhabitants. Located on Multan Road, it offers easy accessibility to the most prominent locations within the city. The project building is spacious and comes equipped with several state-of-the-art residential facilities and a dedicated security system. As such, it perfectly reflects the developer’s commitment to leaving its occupants in want of little else (in terms of living comfort). Revel in the Ever-Lasting Charm of Lahore Lahore, as Pakistan’s perennial cultural capital, has always attracted people from all parts of the country – if not the world. The metropolis simply thrums with an unapologetic brand of electric energy. It might be a tad noisy and too fast-paced at times, but aren’t all the best cities? The outskirts of the Punjabi capital are currently being reinforced with the development of a number of suburban communities geared to provide a green, secure and healthy living environment for their dwellers. These housing projects are ideal for the people who like the comforts of the city but are wary of its clamor. The Multan Road is one of the city’s recently developed residential locations that offers a lot of home ownership potential; seeing as all the best educational and medical institutions have set up their establishments here. Stellar Location Hamza Residencia is built near the Honda Gateway on Multan Road – in the close proximity of a number of communal living facilities. The project, further, is situated near the city entrance, making it the ‘first point of sojourn’ for droves of incoming inter-city traffic (and thereby a convenient convergence point for people with province-wide business interests). To put the project’s positioning into ground perspective, consider its following locational attributes:
  • Opposite to Eden Value Homes
  • Near Orange Line Metro Thokar Station
  • 2-minute drive from Metro Cash & Carry, KFC & Hardees
  • 2-minute drive from Daewoo Main Terminal (Thokar Niaz Baig)
  • 5-minute drive from Defence Road & EME Sector
  • 6-minute drive from Canal View & Tech Society
  • 10-minute drive from Expo Center Lahore Salient Features Like any worthy housing project, Hamza Residencia offers an experience that goes above and beyond in providing residential comfort and convenience. Surveying the structure – and its range of living and recreational amenities (listed below) – it soon becomes clear that the developer did, in fact, put a lot of heart and soul in seeing to its development. Consider the following project features:
  • Vast, Dedicated Parking
  • 24/7 state-of-the-art Security System
  • Restaurant on rooftop
  • Kids play area
  • Gymnasium
  • Prayer room
  • Rooftop garden
  • Cigar lounge
  • In-house clinic for residents
  • High-speed lifts
  • 24/7 generator backup
  • Gas and water supply
  • Lifetime management and maintenance facility
  • Common laundry A project worthy of your investment Given its promising location, contemporary architecture and provision of all conceivable lifestyle amenities, Hamza Residencia presents a great investment option for all categories of buyers. It has all the ingredients to become a lucrative project that offers terrific returns on investment. Some factors that further add to its appeal include:
  • Approved by Lahore Development Authority (LDA)
  • Operational booking office
  • Fast-paced developmental work currently underway
  • Hamza Developers successfully delivered City Star Shopping Center on main Model Town Road, Lahore
  • Exclusively marketed and sold by Zameen. com, ensuring all due diligence in ensuring its quality and reliability has been undertaken

developments.title: Al Hayat Residencia
developments.description:
Al-Hayat Residencia is a sparkling residential complex that is geared towards providing the perfect lifestyle to its residents. It gives them a place to experience the joy of living, an artistic glimpse of ultimate residence where you can spend optimum time with your family. This project offers a chance to turn your dreamy notions of contemporary living into reality by dwelling into its state of the art apartments. What Can You Get? This project consists of six residential blocks and one commercial plaza. The residential blocks are Iris, Bluebell, Lily, Jasmine, Daisy, and Orchid. These blocks contain well-designed apartments with layouts that never sacrifice style and smart utilization of space. The apartment options available are: 1-Bed Apartments 2-Bed Apartments 3-Bed Apartments A Stunning Location Al-Hayat Residencia is in the perfect location for a serene lifestyle with convenient access to all the modern amenities required for comfortable lifestyle. It is located on wildlife park road, off Raiwind Road. This area has been booming when it comes to new projects, with ever increasing demand and prices on the growth side. This project will be no different when it comes to the high returns that can be expected. It is also becoming increasingly populated due to the constant influx of people moving to Lahore for their careers and education as it lies in the junction of universities such as Comsats, University of Lahore, Beaconhouse National University, and University of Central Punjab. Some other benefits of Al-Hayat Residencia
  • Close proximity to Lahore Safari Zoo
  • 2 minutes from Lahore Ring Road
  • 3 minutes from University of Lahore
  • 8 minutes from Shaukat Khanum Cancer Memorial Hospital
  • 25 minutes from Allama Iqbal International Airport Facilities For A Great Lifestyle A great lifestyle is right within reach with Al-Hayat Residencia. The facilities it offers ensure that residents can enjoy a peaceful environment without compromising on any modern conveniences. The facilities and amenities offered here include:
  • E-Access to apartments
  • 24/7 security system & maintenance
  • 24/7 power backup system
  • Gymnasium
  • Cinema
  • Community Center
  • Health & fitness club
  • Firefighting system
  • Underground utilities
  • Spacious parking
  • Parking for visitors & handicapped
  • Parks & children’s play area
  • Shopping mall
  • Central mosque
  • Indoor games
  • Rainwater drainage system Why invest? Al-Hayat Residencia is a wonderful opportunity for investment due to a variety of reasons, including:
  • Rising property prices in the vicinity, as the area has experienced a 45-50% increase in the past 3 years
  • More than 50% return on investment in the next two years expected.
  • It is a secure and gated community
  • Easy installment plan of 48 months
  • It is undergoing massive infrastructural development at a fast pace
  • The project is approved by the Metropolitan Corporation of Lahore and all other relevant authorities.
  • The demand for apartments in Lahore has gone up due to changing preferences, and this project will help meet that demand.
  • It is being exclusively marketed and sold by Zameen. com, which makes it a reliable project which meets a stringent set of international standards.
